To enable this feature, add `css.data` and `js.data` files to a folder that is named with the same name as the page slug and stored in the same directory level:

~~~ .txt
lot\
 └── page\
     ├── blog-page\
     │   ├── css.data
     │   └── js.data
     └── blog-page.page
~~~

Write custom CSS code in `css.data` file, and custom JavaScript code in `js.data` file.

